<bibRefCitation author="Hemming" box="[929,1127,1489,1515]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" refString="Hemming, F. (1964) Annotationes Lepidopterologicae. Part 4. Hepburn &amp; Sons, London, 180 pp." type="book" year="1964">
